version_description: I wrote this song out in the proper key with all the words and chords.

Version for novice players who want to expand on what they already know: chords sound correct but are easy to play / suggestions for playable voicings using only two or three fingers mostly / complete song covered / readably formatted.
Includes the chord chart with the lyrics.

This tab is not a 100% note-for-note transcription, rather an alternative way to play it without the open Gb tuning. These chords should not be barred, letting the Low E, and High B and E always be OPEN. Ex: F#m = 044200, A = 077600, Bm = 099700, etc.
